chatGptLabel: Add SEO and more to article
promptPrefix:
Create in [TARGETLANGUAGE]  separated blocks:
- URL: SEO-friendly short URL or slug.
- Keyword: SEO-friendly focus keyword with less than 3 words
- Title: SEO friendly title with less than 100 characters.
- Excerpt: SEO friendly excerpt (a summary cliffhanger or short invitation to read in less than 155 characters).
- Summary: A very short Summary with less than 300 chars.
- Introduction: An introduction paragraph.
- Conclusion: A conclusion paragraph, thanking for reading and invitation to subscribe and follow.
- Categories: Create at least 10 one-word categories, comma separated (no hashtags and no joined word).
- Emojis: At least 10 emojis.
- Hashtags: At least 10 hashtags that are spaced separated.
- Images: Alternative title name for Images, at least 3.
- Call: Engagin Call to Action at less than 100 characters.
- Subheadings: 2 or 3 posible short subheadings.
- Quotes: 2 or 3 famous quotes.
- Backlinks: Add some links to support the claims.
for this:
[PROMPT]
title: Add SEO and more to article
